{
  "stem": "26576.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we came to Australia March, 1951.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Which was-- we had a very hard time ahead of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I realized it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "First of all, there was no language, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "No matter how many languages you spoke, there was no language.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then, there was no profession and no trade, because Abram never learned any trade.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Although he also went to Ord, but he didn't learn a trade, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was always the type-- a good speaker, but when it came to a trade, he wasn't so good.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So the first years in Australia were very hard for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were-- we had completely no qualification to start a new life in a new country.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were one week only in a house that Jewish welfare had somewhere in Camberwell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then, we got a room in Thornbury.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And-- you know, John was only 10 months when we came to Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I couldn't work, which was really a disaster, because Abram could not make a living.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He worked for big firms, like for small ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was an unemployment then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I mean, it was a lot of unemployed people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And although the people were saying that the times were very good, we couldn't see the good times, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was no any social security.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Now if a migrant doesn't work, he gets social security.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There was no social security.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "If you didn't have money, or if you didn't have work, you didn't eat, simple as that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I can tell you, that many times, we did not have what to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Those were the first years in Australia, which I think really was a very uncomfortable feeling.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Then, if that's not enough, we came at a time-- I wasn't aware, but John got poliomyelitis.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
